Deletes a self-service action

Source: R/servicecatalog_operations.R
servicecatalog_delete_service_action.Rd

Deletes a self-service action.

servicecatalog_delete_service_action(Id, AcceptLanguage)

Arguments

Id

[required] The self-service action identifier. For example, act-fs7abcd89wxyz.
AcceptLanguage

The language code.

  • en - English (default)

  • jp - Japanese

  • zh - Chinese

Request syntax

svc$delete_service_action(
  Id = "string",
  AcceptLanguage = "string"
)
